lead_paragraph: John Daly shot a 2-under 70 on Friday in his PGA Tour Champions debut, leaving him four strokes behind leader Mike Goodes in the Insperity Invitational.

headline.print_headline: John Daly Shoots 2-Under 70 in PGA Tour Champions Debut
